<inglise> 70/372/EEC: Council Decision of 20 July 1970 setting up a Standing Committee for Feeding-stuffs </inglise>
<eesti> N&Otilde;UKOGU OTSUS 70/372/EM&Uuml;, millega luuakse alaline s&ouml;&ouml;dakomitee 20. juuli 1970 </eesti>
<inglise> THE COUNCIL OF THE EUROPEAN COMMUNITIES, </inglise>
<eesti> Euroopa &uuml;henduste n&otilde;ukogu, </eesti>
<inglise> Having regard to the Treaty establishing the European Economic Community; </inglise>
<eesti> v&otilde;ttes arvesse Euroopa Majandus&uuml;henduse asutamislepingut, </eesti>
<inglise> Having regard to the draft decision submitted by the Commission; </inglise>
<eesti> v&otilde;ttes arvesse komisjoni esitatud otsuse eeln&otilde;u </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas the instruments adopted by the Council relating to feeding-stuffs provide, for the purpose of facilitating implementation of such instruments, for a procedure establishing close co-operation between Member States and the Commission; whereas, in order to achieve such co-operation, a Committee should be set up to carry out the duties devolving upon it under those instruments; </inglise>
<eesti> ning arvestades, et: n&otilde;ukogu vastuv&otilde;etud &otilde;igusaktides s&ouml;&ouml;tade kohta s&auml;testatakse k&otilde;nealuste aktide rakendamise lihtsustamiseks menetlus, millega luuakse tihe koost&ouml;&ouml; liikmesriikide ja komisjoni vahel; sellise koost&ouml;&ouml; saavutamiseks tuleks luua komitee, mis t&auml;idaks nendest &otilde;igusaktidest tulenevaid &uuml;lesandeid; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas it is desirable that such co-operation should extend to all fields covered by those instruments; whereas that Committee should accordingly be empowered to consider any question relating to such fields; </inglise>
<eesti> on soovitav, et selline koost&ouml;&ouml; laieneks k&otilde;ikidele k&otilde;nealuste &otilde;igusaktidega h&otilde;lmatud valdkondadele; k&otilde;nealusel komiteel v&otilde;iks vastavalt olla volitused k&auml;sitleda k&otilde;iki nende valdkondadega seotud k&uuml;simusi; </eesti>
<inglise> HAS DECIDED AS FOLLOWS: </inglise>
<eesti> ON VASTU V&Otilde;TNUD J&Auml;RGMISE OTSUSE. </eesti>
<inglise> Article 1 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 1 </eesti>
<inglise> A Standing Committee for Feeding-stuffs (hereinafter called the "Committee") is hereby set up and shall consist of representatives of the Member States with a representative of the Commission as Chairman. </inglise>
<eesti> Moodustatakse alaline s&ouml;&ouml;dakomitee (edaspidi "komitee"), mis koosneb liikmesriikide esindajatest ja mille eesistujaks on komisjoni esindaja. </eesti>
<inglise> Article 2 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 2 </eesti>
<inglise> The Committee shall, in the cases and under the conditions provided for therein, carry out the duties devolving upon it under the instruments relating to feeding-stuffs adopted by the Council. </inglise>
<eesti> Komitee t&auml;idab s&ouml;&ouml;tasid k&auml;sitlevatest n&otilde;ukogu vastuv&otilde;etud &otilde;igusaktidest tulenevaid &uuml;lesandeid nendes aktides etten&auml;htud juhtudel ja tingimustel. </eesti>
<inglise> It may, moreover, consider any other question arising under such instruments and referred to it by the Chairman either on his own initiative or at the request of a Member State. </inglise>
<eesti> Komitee v&otilde;ib k&auml;sitleda k&otilde;iki nendest &otilde;igusaktidest tulenevaid muid k&uuml;simusi, mille komitee esimees on suunanud talle omal algatusel v&otilde;i liikmesriigi esindaja taotlusel. </eesti>
<inglise> Article 3 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 3 </eesti>
<inglise> The Committee shall adopt its own rules of procedure. </inglise>
<eesti> Komitee v&otilde;tab vastu oma t&ouml;&ouml;korra. </eesti>
<inglise> Done at Brussels, 20 July 1970. </inglise>
<eesti> Br&uuml;ssel, 20. juuli 1970 </eesti>
<inglise> For the Council </inglise>
<eesti> N&otilde;ukogu nimel </eesti>
<inglise> The President </inglise>
<eesti> president </eesti>
<inglise> W. SCHEEL </inglise>
